  "text": "Apoe 2/2 mice on a C57BL/6 background and WT C57BL/6 mice were purchased from Beijing University (Beijing, China). The Pdcd4 2/2 mice on C57BL/6 background were generated as described previously [CITATION_1] and were mated with the Apoe 2/2 mice to obtain the Pdcd4 2/2 Apoe 2/2 mice. All animal study protocols were approved by the Animal Care and Utilization Committee of Shandong University.",
